Materialization of Kim Il Sung's Idea of Believing in People as in Heaven Called for
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, April 14 (KCNA) -- Korean-style socialism has fully displayed its advantages and vitality generation after generation as it is a peculiar one, an embodiment of President Kim Il Sung's idea of believing in people as in Heaven. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
